"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612659\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612659\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dte1665702632952.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dte1665702632952.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dte1665702632952.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dte1665702632952\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The image that is displayed as the button or tab.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ImgDefault=\"@ImageFile</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">^GlyphName\"</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dte1665702632952__section_irm_pjf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d373485e57\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dte1665702632952__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dte1665702632952__section_qzw_qjf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d373485e103\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dte1665702632952__p_d104882e1_d104883e1_d104884e1\">Use this property if you want to represent a button or\n        tab as an image. The size of the image affects the size of widget. Uniface looks for images\n        in the directory specified by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Images</span> setting in the [paths] section\n        of <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dte1665702632952__p_d104885e1_d104886e1_d104887e1\">For command buttons, this property only works if the\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> property is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dte1665702632952__p_d104888e1_d104889e1_d104890e1\">For the TabEx widget, specifying a value for this\n        property overrides the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Colors</span> property, and enables the\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Active Image</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hover Image</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab\n          Strip Image</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Scroll Buttons</span> properties to work (if\n        defined).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dte1665702632952__section_mct_sjf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d373485e145\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dte1665702632952__pre_zzs_tjf_ywb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"ImgDefault=@filesave.png\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dte1665702632952__section_evz_tjf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d373485e154\">Example: Specifying Images for Tabs</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dte1665702632952__p_d104897e1_d104898e1_d104899e1\">The following ProcScript code sets the images to\n        display for a tab widget in its normal state, when a mouse cursor hovers over it, and when\n        it is selected:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dte1665702632952__pre_lmb_xjf_ywb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vProperties = \"\"; string variable to contain widget properties\n; Create a list of widget properties\nputitem/id vProperties,\"imgdefault\", \"@gradient_default_blue.jpg\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"imghover\",\"@gradient_hover_white.bmp\"\nputitem/id vProperties,\"imgselect\", \"@gradient_select_green.bmp\"\n; Assign the properties list to the Tab widget\n$fieldproperties(TAB_FLD) = vProperties</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"dte1665702632952__fig_d104900e1_d104901e1_d104902e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Images for Tabs</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Images for tabs\" class=\"image\" id=\"dte1665702632952__image_hzm_yjf_ywb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/tabimages.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dte1665702632952__section_h2c_zjf_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d373485e179\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dte1665702632952__ul_qxj_1kf_ywb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dte1665702632952__li_d41852e1_d41853e1_d41854e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dte1665702632952__li_d41855e1_d41856e1_d41857e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dte1665702632952__li_d41858e1_d41859e1_d41860e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/daw1665702633024.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Active Image (ImgSelect)</a><p>The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aww1665702633098.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Hover Image (ImgHover)</a><p>The image that is displayed when the mouse cursor rests on the button or tab.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cms1665702633168.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Focus Image (ImgFocus)</a><p>The image that is displayed when the button field has focus.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qug1665702641707.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tab Strip Image (TabStripImage)</a><p>The Tab Strip Image widget property specifies an image that can be used as a background for the complete horizontal tab strip.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbl1665703095768.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ScrollButtons</a><p>Images to use for the left and right scroll buttons.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tlk1704711601774.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Specify the Location of Image Files</a><p>Images that are specified with the @ sign (for example, @donald.gif) are loaded from the file system. By default, Uniface tries to load image files from the working directory, but you can specify a different default directory.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zrt1665702757821.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Images</a><p>Specifies the name of the directory where image files are stored. You can specify more than one directory by using a comma-separated list.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/btj1665702631955.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Representation</a><p>This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612659\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612659\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Default Image (ImgDefault) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The image that is displayed as the button or tab. ImgDefault=\"@ImageFile | ^GlyphName\" Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description Use this property if you want to represent a button or tab as an image. The size of the image affects the size of widget. Uniface looks for images in the directory specified by the Images setting in the [paths] section of usys.ini . For command buttons, this property only works if the Representation property is set to Uniface . For the TabEx widget, specifying a value for this property overrides the Tab Colors property, and enables the Active Image , Hover Image , Tab Strip Image , Scroll Buttons properties to work (if defined). Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"ImgDefault=@filesave.png\" Copy Example: Specifying Images for Tabs The following ProcScript code sets the images to display for a tab widget in its normal state, when a mouse cursor hovers over it, and when it is selected: vProperties = \"\"; string variable to contain widget properties ; Create a list of widget properties putitem/id vProperties,\"imgdefault\", \"@gradient_default_blue.jpg\" putitem/id vProperties,\"imghover\",\"@gradient_hover_white.bmp\" putitem/id vProperties,\"imgselect\", \"@gradient_select_green.bmp\" ; Assign the properties list to the Tab widget $fieldproperties(TAB_FLD) = vProperties Copy Figure 1. Images for Tabs Applies To CommandButton utab (Tab) utabex (TabEx) Related Links Active Image (ImgSelect) The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected. Hover Image (ImgHover) The image that is displayed when the mouse cursor rests on the button or tab. Focus Image (ImgFocus) The image that is displayed when the button field has focus. Tab Strip Image (TabStripImage) The Tab Strip Image widget property specifies an image that can be used as a background for the complete horizontal tab strip. ScrollButtons Images to use for the left and right scroll buttons. Specify the Location of Image Files Images that are specified with the @ sign (for example, @donald.gif) are loaded from the file system. By default, Uniface tries to load image files from the working directory, but you can specify a different default directory. Images Specifies the name of the directory where image files are stored. You can specify more than one directory by using a comma-separated list. Representation This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}